<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-786] JUnit @Category are not taken into account if forkMode=always</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-786</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Selection by groups works if forkMode=once or none. Whith forkMode=always, it seems that all tests are executed.&lt;br/&gt;
See attachment for a test case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
